GothicSketches <p>//--//--GOTHICSKETCHES--\\--\\</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=thehawk>The Hawk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Pre-Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(3/21/02 7:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=568.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Little Help...</span><hr size=1> I'm not pro but I can still help.<br>
<br>
First of all, you have the title right? So, what's the genre of your animation? Is it a drama? Comedy?<br>
<br>
The type of character you're going to use depends a lot in this. You cannot have a drama with little and cute Chibi characters!!. I really don't know how to help you more if you don't give me a little spoiler of your work.<br>
<br>
BUT, if it is an Animation, then you should take the tutorial of PolyKarbon oriented to Storyboards.<br>
<br>
I know it wasn't a great help, but it's a start. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ugothicsketches.showPublicProfile?language=EN>GothicSketches</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.salon.com/books/feature/1999/08/05/goth/goth.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Pre-Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(3/21/02 7:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=568.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.salon.com/books/feature/1999/08/05/goth/goth.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Little Help...</span><hr size=1> Hawk-<br>
<br>
The genre of this series is sort of a strange one, Gothic/Action/Drama...don't ask. It's not with cute little chibi characters either...infact the three main characters are at least 18...Carmine is the main character<br>
